---
title: Turkish-Spiced Beef Tacos with Hummus & Cucumber Salsa
description: We’ve given these tacos a little Turkish twist. These eye-catching handheld delights tick all the boxes – saucy mince, crisp veggies, and our secret ingredient, chermoula spice blend, for loads of flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/turkish-spiced-beef-tacos-e2236c2b.jpg
